{"tid":2497293,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"英華小學前校長林浣心送左間屋俾PK鄧","createTime":"2021-04-20T11:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T12:27:07.000Z","uid":285843,"like":8,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd4e2d9d14ccd8060551e525e3b5c7f04c9025b","tid":2497293,"uid":285843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"呢隻口裡愛國<br />\n退左休即刻移居英國嘅林浣心<br />\n扮晒愛學生 假撚到仆街<br />\n早兩年好多英華學生同舊生被捕被告被害<br />\n佢就視而不見 仲堅定撐狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家退左休得閒就翻香港同PK鄧飲下茶<br />\n仲送埋間手作嘅屋俾呢隻畜牲<br />\n簡直係教育界嘅恥辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYiSR7sAfstZh4qNJF62pcWGWcYJ8ajssnRHiUcXF9zKN?filename=j2tWvFR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj2tWvFR.jpg&h=5b64b0cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTEv7r8nidp9v5qFKp3c1togPwG7VKAZ33s1vxHaSdRJn?filename=ngBMSUd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngBMSUd.jpg&h=9ebb58c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaAjQZVw4haTmqHZkzRsroEVgJoX3m7ZdamgVDGMAn6Y1?filename=tddoaFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtddoaFU.jpg&h=0e24e5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTNbGvcQBSJPV3JKdLbtr95w3hPz5zfC91G9Er9KaULN4?filename=uaHsCkU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuaHsCkU.jpg&h=0fc5c1af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【校長訪問】放下45年教鞭到英國退休　前英華校長林浣心：我體會做媽媽的感覺</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2813406/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2813406%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=a41dc215\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2813406/</a>"},{"pid":"999e55f783cb1cdb7df1ec5b09cc9f21429f970c","tid":2497293,"uid